d not only by internal dynamical\nprocesses, but also by the specific evolutionary history of their host\ngalaxies. These results emphasize that $N$-body studies with realistic stellar\nphysics are crucial to understanding the evolution and present-day properties\nof GC systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Mar 2022 18:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 24 Feb 2023 01:31:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-01"}
