 tuple for bid-discount/pacing first-price\nauctions. Meanwhile, when buyers do not take strategic behaviors, we exploit\nthe dominance relationships of these mechanisms by revealing their intrinsic\nstructures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Mar 2022 05:53:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 5 May 2022 04:10:43 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 7 Jul 2022 05:36:42 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 8 Jul 2022 15:29:51 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 6 Dec 2022 02:56:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-07"}
