plex phase profiles, as in the case of phase-only masks\nand optical vortices, a significantly challenging task for traditional\nimplementations at optical frequencies based on intensity measurements aided\nwith interferometric techniques.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Mar 2022 10:18:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-01"}
