lt casts doubt on the universal applicability of\nnitrogen-based strong-line metallicity indicators derived in the local\nuniverse.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Mar 2022 13:44:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-25"}
